## Development URLs

- Frontend: http://localhost:3000
- Backend API: http://localhost:3001
- API Docs: http://localhost:3001/docs

## API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint        | Description              | Protected |
|--------|----------------|--------------------------|-----------|
| POST   | /auth/register | Register a new user      | No        |
| POST   | /auth/login    | Authenticate a user      | No        |
| GET    | /users         | List all users           | Yes       |
| GET    | /users/:id     | Get a user by ID         | Yes       |

## Scripts

- `pnpm dev` - Start frontend and backend in development mode
- `pnpm build` - Build both applications
- `pnpm docker:up` - Start Docker services
- `pnpm docker:down` - Stop Docker services

## Authentication

The application uses JWT-based authentication. After logging in, the access token is stored in `localStorage` and automatically attached to API requests via an Axios interceptor.

